Quick Reference: Critical Deadlines

**Form I-9 Compliance**

• Section 1: BY FIRST DAY of work

• Section 2: Within 3 BUSINESS DAYS of hire

**Final Paycheck**

• Involuntary: IMMEDIATELY

• Voluntary: Within 72 hours (or on last day if 48+ hours notice)

**Training Requirements**

• Sexual Harassment: Every 2 years (biennial)

• Workplace Violence (SB 553): Annual

**Retention Periods**

• Personnel File: 4 years from separation

• I-9 Forms: 3 years from hire OR 1 year from separation (whichever is
LATER)

• Medical Records: 30 years per Cal/OSHA
